headline.main: Argentine FA Election Scuppered by Rogue Ballot
headline.print_headline: Argentine FA Election Scuppered by Rogue Ballot

docs.snippet: The Argentine Football Association’s (AFA) bid to hold a democratic election for the first time in 36 years ended in farce on Thursday when organisers discovered an extra vote among the 75 cast by the assembly....
docs.lead_paragraph: The Argentine Football Association’s (AFA) bid to hold a democratic election for the first time in 36 years ended in farce on Thursday when organisers discovered an extra vote among the 75 cast by the assembly.
